    <li class="text input optional" id="recipe_doc_input"><label class=" label" for="recipe_doc">Doc</label><textarea id="recipe_doc" name="recipe[doc]" rows="20">curl -u user:pass https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/ORG/e/ENV/virtualhosts/default &gt; vh.json

Now look at &quot;vh.json&quot;:

{
  &quot;hostAliases&quot; : [ &quot;ORG-ENV.apigee.net&quot; ],
  &quot;interfaces&quot; : [ ],
  &quot;name&quot; : &quot;default&quot;,
  &quot;port&quot; : &quot;80&quot;
}

Now edit the file to add another host alias:

{
  &quot;hostAliases&quot; : [ &quot;ORG-ENV.apigee.net&quot;, &quot;api.your.name.here.com&quot; ],
  &quot;interfaces&quot; : [ ],
  &quot;name&quot; : &quot;default&quot;,
  &quot;port&quot; : &quot;80&quot;
}

And now replace it:

curl -u user:pass https://api.enterprise.apigee.com/v1/o/ORG/e/ENV/virtualhosts/default -H &quot;Content-Type: application/json&quot; -X PUT -T vh.json</textarea>

